ble for issue comments.\\n\\n### Generating Metadata\\n\\nGenerates metadata for a single library coordinate. If `agentAllowedPackages` is provided, a new user-code-filter.json will be created or updated from those packages or from package roots derived from the resolved library JAR.\\n\\n- `coordinates`: group:artifact:version (single coordinate only)\\n- `agentAllowedPackages`: comma-separated package list, `fromJar`, or `-` for none\\n\\nExamples:\\n   ```console\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=fromJar\\n   ./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=org.postgresql:postgresql:42.7.3 --agentAllowedPackages=org.example.app,com.acme.service\\n\\n[93 more lines in file. Use offset=201 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777432551541}}\nhuman-intervention-logs/org.hsqldb:hsqldb:2.4.1/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-04-29T03-17-35-576545Z.log:341:[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_027b4c9c3cbf53050169f177e6d95481a189bde54fb23e088f\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp8XfniHMDblh1sGqDVrQCvn8Ui_a16SqiuQBKVs2FUxfvMxJWuYCPA3zU5c7oj8r9N7Q2fZ6I6jfWzjsWRCHDTGrMEZ_tRBgb8ex1ZYhRW7t-H3orUiFtRMmcPAt6TPSpSGUN5ipPaDAEfM6aW_iioVYDkd7k7JLS858CHCpYorBTmU6lk-rV2a1Rzz4FcMSqSUYGtAn6NAU7Fic0W99zpjvUonyQTJcaZA9bEPSwJsoYNiCLZ1anhh-tFMj2MwO_9xLJWzFzl50TRU-_YZ3ycYeD05nAdiCQ52zzdwStTXo0mWi5XRsM7P4hEkmFW323Fwz5UfM9P_P7exqHjQjxtqJrwPC1PsVy5PbodsM9qsLfJP6eHFGlIsyFJotJ49tmTozFN-ba_MABIYz5QIbxn70Md6s81nLtT19tagmJb4XyhITJhAj6q4SaGGJS24c0NPMlYambb53YrhHOq_W_HoyScmtiiH4FZJGpg2qChVUPB-qxwSoGnPWJwrcQYGZ-3oTSNbIWCmsEA3xMxN16q5Mt7cLKn89RcX99iwz6WOOSR6qnKbdPaTcsR7Q7iP2JCziDOvdzdDGMPi9BHM-GymI7IYwoPqiQX0zQLTMH9gcya6Q6PMPjiZZ-gJR_gPRzNUo521OxlFovrYDt8hzqsWyFFoE9Oe