 file:\\n  - `tests/src/org.hsqldb/hsqldb/2.4.1/src/test/java/org_hsqldb/hsqldb/JDBCParameterMetaDataTest.java`\\n- Added reachability metadata for the active class:\\n  - `metadata/org.hsqldb/hsqldb/2.4.1/reachability-metadata.json`\\n  - Registers `org.hsqldb.jdbc.JDBCParameterMetaData` declared methods for reflective access.\\n\\nThe new test obtains `JDBCParameterMetaData` through the public JDBC `PreparedStatement#getParameterMetaData()` API and calls `toString()` to reach the remaining reflective dynamic-access sites in `toStringImpl`.\\n\\nCommit created:\\n- `c21bcc7303 Add HSQLDB parameter metadata coverage`\\n\\nPer instruction, I did not compile or run tests.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_027b4c9c3cbf53050169f1784dcf5c81a190ebed31205d1070\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 633, \"output\": 189, \"cacheRead\": 30208, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 31030, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777432652620, \"responseId\": \"resp_027b4c9c3cbf53050169f1784d144081a18d294d60597edc3a\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
